<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
     
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
     
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
      <title>Thank You</title>
      <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: #121a26;
            /* Very dark navy for less strain */
            color: #cbd5e1;
            /* Soft light blue-gray text */
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .thank-you-card {
            background: #1f2a3a;
            /* Dark slate blue */
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .thank-you-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
        }

        .thank-you-card .checkmark {
            font-size: 56px;
            color: #56b6c2;
            /* Soft teal */
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .thank-you-card h1 {
            color: #e0e7ff;
            /* Light periwinkle */
            font-size: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .thank-you-card p {
            color: #a0aec0;
            /* Muted gray-blue */
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 34px;
        }

        .thank-you-card a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            background-color: #56b6c2;
            /* same teal accent */
            color: #1a202c;
            /* almost black text for contrast */
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(86, 182, 194, 0.5);
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .thank-you-card a:hover {
            background-color: #3a96a8;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(58, 150, 168, 0.7);
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .thank-you-card {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .thank-you-card h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .thank-you-card p {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

      <div class="thank-you-card" role="region" aria-label="Thank you message">
            <div class="checkmark" aria-hidden="true">✓</div>
            <h1>Thank You!</h1>
            <p>Thanks for contacting us.<br>We’ll reach out to you soon.</p>
            <a href="/" aria-label="Back to Home">← Back to Home</a>
          </div>

</body>

</html>